  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a Slayer of Ramsgate, you are all that stands between your world and the Behemoths that seek to devour it. Hunt huge monsters, alongside other Slayers on any platform, and craft awesome gear in this stylish free-to-play co-op action RPG.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Behemoth Undertaking</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect the Shattered Isles from over 40 different monstrous Behemoths in thrilling and rewarding boss-fight encounters. Combine preparation, skill, reflexes, and grit to save humanity from these insatiable beasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/6a13238d3c20371b6c09a4fb575bdb60.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/6a13238d3c20371b6c09a4fb575bdb60.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/6a13238d3c20371b6c09a4fb575bdb60.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Slayer Is Only As Good As Its Weapon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master and level up an arsenal of unique weapons, each with unique Legendary abilities and Talents to help you slay Behemoths with power and style. Swap in your subweapon to harness powerful combos and give you the edge over your quarry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/0714ff8bf4d8225f5bffb15fcdd9a0fb.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=660 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/0714ff8bf4d8225f5bffb15fcdd9a0fb.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/0714ff8bf4d8225f5bffb15fcdd9a0fb.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take Sweet Revenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harvest parts from slain Behemoths to craft, upgrade, and optimize your armour, using Cells to activate perks and unlock the true potential of your gear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/1e8c16696f00d69291a7532688a09a5b.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/1e8c16696f00d69291a7532688a09a5b.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/1e8c16696f00d69291a7532688a09a5b.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>There’s No “I” In Slayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re not in this fight alone. Team up with other Slayers to take down Behemoths, with seamless cross-play and cross-progression, powered by Epic accounts. Join Parties or Guilds to find and create a community with like-minded Slayers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/af3906e8dad49671a2da2f8a9c35726f.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/af3906e8dad49671a2da2f8a9c35726f.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/af3906e8dad49671a2da2f8a9c35726f.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Slay Your Way</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the game modes and challenges that suit your playstyle:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Hunting Grounds</strong> are open worlds, where you can hunt a variety of Behemoths at a skill level of your choosing</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escalations</strong> will test your grit with relentless back-to-back challenges, in a chaotic roguelike environment with experimental builds and modifiers </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trials</strong> pit you against a Behemoth in a gladiatorial arena, with unique challenges and rewards, including a leaderboard</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not for the faint of heart, <strong>Gauntlet</strong> offers 600+ levels of increasing challenges each season, for you and your teammates, with bragging rights for the most accomplished Guilds </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/818fb64071ef195213a10b3749ca3328.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=614 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/818fb64071ef195213a10b3749ca3328.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/818fb64071ef195213a10b3749ca3328.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What Kind of Slayer Are You?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and express what kind of Slayer you want to be with over a dozen different ways to customize your character and a rich catalog of cosmetics. Combined with hundreds of nodes in the Slayer’s Path skill tree, there’s no limit to what kind of Slayer you can be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/5677fcdf48515b0bf0c12a0676b35248.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=704 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/5677fcdf48515b0bf0c12a0676b35248.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/5677fcdf48515b0bf0c12a0676b35248.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World Worth Slaying For</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Shattered Isles is always growing and evolving. Each Season brings new content and features. And live events showcase limited-time quests and content, new and classic cosmetics, and gameplay boosts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/9a40e524dd9af8ae98d67c40a235c57a.avif?t=1748587583\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras_big/9a40e524dd9af8ae98d67c40a235c57a.avif?t=1748587583 width=800 height=244 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a Slayer of Ramsgate, you are all that stands between your world and the Behemoths that seek to devour it. Hunt huge monsters, alongside other Slayers on any platform, and craft awesome gear in this stylish free-to-play co-op action RPG.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Behemoth Undertaking</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect the Shattered Isles from over 40 different monstrous Behemoths in thrilling and rewarding boss-fight encounters. Combine preparation, skill, reflexes, and grit to save humanity from these insatiable beasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/6a13238d3c20371b6c09a4fb575bdb60.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/6a13238d3c20371b6c09a4fb575bdb60.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/6a13238d3c20371b6c09a4fb575bdb60.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Slayer Is Only As Good As Its Weapon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master and level up an arsenal of unique weapons, each with unique Legendary abilities and Talents to help you slay Behemoths with power and style. Swap in your subweapon to harness powerful combos and give you the edge over your quarry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/0714ff8bf4d8225f5bffb15fcdd9a0fb.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=660 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/0714ff8bf4d8225f5bffb15fcdd9a0fb.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/0714ff8bf4d8225f5bffb15fcdd9a0fb.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take Sweet Revenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harvest parts from slain Behemoths to craft, upgrade, and optimize your armour, using Cells to activate perks and unlock the true potential of your gear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/1e8c16696f00d69291a7532688a09a5b.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/1e8c16696f00d69291a7532688a09a5b.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/1e8c16696f00d69291a7532688a09a5b.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>There’s No “I” In Slayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re not in this fight alone. Team up with other Slayers to take down Behemoths, with seamless cross-play and cross-progression, powered by Epic accounts. Join Parties or Guilds to find and create a community with like-minded Slayers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/af3906e8dad49671a2da2f8a9c35726f.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/af3906e8dad49671a2da2f8a9c35726f.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/af3906e8dad49671a2da2f8a9c35726f.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Slay Your Way</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the game modes and challenges that suit your playstyle:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Hunting Grounds</strong> are open worlds, where you can hunt a variety of Behemoths at a skill level of your choosing</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escalations</strong> will test your grit with relentless back-to-back challenges, in a chaotic roguelike environment with experimental builds and modifiers </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trials</strong> pit you against a Behemoth in a gladiatorial arena, with unique challenges and rewards, including a leaderboard</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not for the faint of heart, <strong>Gauntlet</strong> offers 600+ levels of increasing challenges each season, for you and your teammates, with bragging rights for the most accomplished Guilds </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/818fb64071ef195213a10b3749ca3328.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=614 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/818fb64071ef195213a10b3749ca3328.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/818fb64071ef195213a10b3749ca3328.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What Kind of Slayer Are You?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and express what kind of Slayer you want to be with over a dozen different ways to customize your character and a rich catalog of cosmetics. Combined with hundreds of nodes in the Slayer’s Path skill tree, there’s no limit to what kind of Slayer you can be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/5677fcdf48515b0bf0c12a0676b35248.poster.avif?t=1748587583\" width=704 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/5677fcdf48515b0bf0c12a0676b35248.webm?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/5677fcdf48515b0bf0c12a0676b35248.mp4?t=1748587583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World Worth Slaying For</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Shattered Isles is always growing and evolving. Each Season brings new content and features. And live events showcase limited-time quests and content, new and classic cosmetics, and gameplay boosts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras/9a40e524dd9af8ae98d67c40a235c57a.avif?t=1748587583\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/331370/extras_big/9a40e524dd9af8ae98d67c40a235c57a.avif?t=1748587583 width=800 height=244 /></span></p>",
